title: GOP aims to restart ethics complaint into Democrat senator
text: ST. PAUL, Minn. (AP) - Republicans are renewing their call for an ethics investigation into a Democrat with ties to an embattled nonprofit. Senate Republicans have repeatedly pushed for a hearing into whether Sen. Jeff Hayden benefited financially from misspending at Community Action Minneapolis.
